[I] Advanced Profiling and Analytics for AMD Hardware

[T] ROCm Compute Profiler is a system performance profiling tool for machine
[T] learning/HPC workloads running on AMD MI GPUs. The tool presently targets
[T] usage on MI100, MI200, and MI300 accelerators.

